{
  "id": "xhs-video",
  "platform": "xiaohongshu",
  "mode": "video",
  "name": "小红书 · 视频笔记",
  "steps": [
    {
      "id": "title",
      "name": "标题生成",
      "type": "title",
      "needs": [],
      "promptTemplate": "xiaohongshu/video/title.md",
      "humanGate": true,
      "defaultProvider": "cli-claude"
    },
    {
      "id": "content",
      "name": "口播稿生成",
      "type": "content",
      "needs": [
        "title"
      ],
      "promptTemplate": "xiaohongshu/video/content.md",
      "defaultProvider": "cli-claude"
    },
    {
      "use": "cover",
      "promptTemplate": "xiaohongshu/video/cover.md",
      "aspects": [
        "3:4",
        "9:16",
        "1:1"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "video",
      "name": "分镜与剪映草稿",
      "type": "video",
      "needs": [
        "content"
      ],
      "promptTemplate": "xiaohongshu/video/storyboard.md",
      "defaultProvider": "cli-gemini",
      "post": "jianying-draft"
    },
    "review"
  ],
  "notes": [
    "视频时长建议 30-90 秒，信息密度高于抖音",
    "标题不超过 20 字，封面与标题信息一致",
    "正文描述带 3-6 个话题标签",
    "封面 3:4，避免纯视频截帧（建议设计感封面）",
    "严禁站外引流（微信号/二维码）"
  ],
  "options": [
    {
      "id": "aspect",
      "default": "3:4",
      "aspects": [
        "3:4",
        "9:16",
        "1:1"
      ]
    },
    {
      "id": "titleMaxLen",
      "label": "标题字数上限",
      "type": "number",
      "default": "20",
      "min": 8,
      "max": 80
    },
    {
      "id": "contentLen",
      "label": "正文/脚本字数",
      "type": "number",
      "default": "300",
      "min": 80,
      "max": 4000,
      "step": 50
    }
  ]
}
